manifests.contents:
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "SolanaDiscordWalletTracker"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "SolanaDiscordWalletTracker"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true

[dependencies]
dotenv = "0.15.0"
env_logger = "0.10.0"
json = "0.12.4"
log = "0.4.17"
prettytable-rs = "0.10.0"
reqwest = "0.11.14"
serde_json = "1.0.48"
solana-client = "1.14.12"
solana-sdk = "1.14.13"
solana-transaction-status = "1.14.13"

[dependencies.chrono]
version = "0.4"
features = ["clock"]
default-features = false

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.104"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.serenity]
version = "0.11.5"
features = ["client", "gateway", "rustls_backend", "framework", "standard_framework", "model", "cache"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1"
features = ["full"]
